## Part 5 — DAX: Calculated Columns

### 5.1 QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION

```dax
-- Classifies each run as Scheduled or Manual
-- Requires relationship to ENABLED_SCHEDULE_DETIALED_SUMMARY via AS_APPLICATION_ID
Trigger_Type =
IF(
    COUNTROWS( RELATEDTABLE( ENABLED_SCHEDULE_DETIALED_SUMMARY ) ) > 0,
    "Scheduled",
    "Manual"
)
```

```dax
-- Runtime bucket for Job Runs distribution chart. FUL_RUN_TIME in seconds [CONFIRM]
Runtime_Bucket =
VAR Mins = QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION[FUL_RUN_TIME] / 60
RETURN
    SWITCH( TRUE(),
        Mins <= 1,  "0–1 min",
        Mins <= 5,  "1–5 min",
        Mins <= 15, "5–15 min",
        Mins <= 30, "15–30 min",
                    "30+ min"
    )

Runtime_Bucket_Sort =
SWITCH( QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION[Runtime_Bucket],
    "0–1 min",   1,
    "1–5 min",   2,
    "5–15 min",  3,
    "15–30 min", 4,
    "30+ min",   5
)
```

```dax
-- Hour of day for Wait Time by Hour chart
Run_Hour = HOUR( QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION[START_DT] )
```

```dax
-- Binary error flag. [CONFIRM exact STATUS value]
Is_Error = IF( QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION[STATUS] = "Error", 1, 0 )
```

```dax
-- H:MM:SS formatted columns
Runtime_Formatted =
VAR TotalSec = QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION[FUL_RUN_TIME]
VAR H = INT( TotalSec / 3600 )
VAR M = INT( MOD( TotalSec, 3600 ) / 60 )
VAR S = INT( MOD( TotalSec, 60 ) )
RETURN FORMAT( H, "0" ) & ":" & FORMAT( M, "00" ) & ":" & FORMAT( S, "00" )

Wait_Time_Formatted =
VAR TotalSec = QUEUE_WORKER_APPLICATION[QUEUE_TIME]
VAR H = INT( TotalSec / 3600 )
VAR M = INT( MOD( TotalSec, 3600 ) / 60 )
VAR S = INT( MOD( TotalSec, 60 ) )
RETURN FORMAT( H, "0" ) & ":" & FORMAT( M, "00" ) & ":" & FORMAT( S, "00" )

-- Total duration column for sort ordering
Total_Duration_Seconds =
