### 6.4 Workflows Measures (refined in V3)

#### L2 Base — existing (unchanged)

```dax
Workflow Total_Base =
DISTINCTCOUNT( AYX_PROD_APPS_COLLECTION_SUMMARY[AS_APPLICATION_ID] )

Workflow Scheduled_Base =
CALCULATE( DISTINCTCOUNT( ENABLED_SCHEDULE_DETIALED_SUMMARY[AS_APPLICATION_ID] ) )

Workflow Unscheduled_Base =
